comments: Smart (BOS) establishes legal position in Butler's (MIA) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Iguodala (MIA) makes incidental contact to Tatum's (BOS) body after he releases his jump shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) is in the lane without actively guarding for longer than three seconds.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact to Smart's (BOS) arm that does not affect his SQBR during his drive.
Adebayo (MIA) cleanly deflects the pass to Hayward (BOS), any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Brown (BOS) makes marginal contact to Dragic's (MIA) body at the end of his drive.
Hayward (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in Dragic's (MIA) path and does not deliver contact.
Butler (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position defending Walker's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) lifts his pivot prior to the start of his dribble.
Herro (MIA) legally contests the shot attempt by Tatum (BOS).
Smart (BOS) places a hand/arm to Herro's (MIA) side during his drive but he is able to move through the contact.
Tatum (BOS) cleanly deflects the pass to Butler (MIA), any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.

Replay review of the foul called on Butler (MIA) pursuant to a coachs challenge was deemed successful. Butler (MIA) makes contact with the ball when defending Tatums (BOS) driving shot attempt. Since the ball was loose at the point of interruption, a jump ball was held at center circle to resume play.
Iguodala (MIA) legally contests Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center it was determined the on-court ruling of Celtics' ball would stand.
Herro (MIA) legally contests the shot attempt by Brown (BOS).
Butler (MIA) is already in Hayward's (BOS) path during the pick and establishes his screening position and absorbs the contact.
Smart (BOS) and Herro (MIA) engage and disengage off ball.
Smart (BOS) makes contact to Herro's (MIA) arm during his drive to the basket affecting his SQBR.
Walker (BOS) gathers the ball and begins his upward shooting motion and Butler (MIA) reaches in and makes hand on ball contact to deflect the ball away.
Hayward (BOS) briefly grasps Butler's (MIA) arm off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).

Iguodala (MIA) establishes his legal guarding position and is extending his hands into a vertical position when contesting Walker's (BOS) shot attempt.  Any ensuing contact is created by Walker jumping forward towards the basket on his shot.
Herro (MIA) makes marginal contact to Theis (BOS) defending the play at the basket.
Walker (BOS) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Butler (MIA) and Brown (BOS) engage and disengage as they go for the pass.
